00:18.000 --> 00:21.200
DON'T GIVE ME ANY OF THAT
"I'M OKAY, YOU'RE OKAY" CRAP!

00:21.200 --> 00:23.100
NOTHING'S OKAY, OKAY?!

00:23.600 --> 00:25.000
COPY THAT, CHIEF.

00:25.000 --> 00:27.500
THE FIRE CHIEF SAYS
THE OFFICE DOOR IS BARRICADED,

00:27.500 --> 00:30.000
AND THEY NEED TIME.
HEAR THAT, TYLER?

00:30.000 --> 00:31.900
BUY US SOME TIME.
OKAY.

00:32.800 --> 00:34.300
(amplified voice)
I HEAR YOU, RUBEN.

00:34.300 --> 00:35.800
WHY DON'T YOU CLIMB
BACK IN THE WINDOW

00:35.800 --> 00:38.000
AND TELL ME
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND?
WHAT'S ON MY MIND?

00:38.000 --> 00:41.000
YOU WANT TO KNOW?

00:41.100 --> 00:43.800
PERSONAL PORTABLE PHONES...

00:43.800 --> 00:46.100
SMALL ENOUGH TO FIT
IN A LARGE BRIEFCASE.

00:46.700 --> 00:49.500
I LOST EVERY PENNY I HAD
ON THAT DAMN COMPANY.

00:49.500 --> 00:52.500
WHAT AN IDIOT. WHO WANTS
TO CARRY AROUND A TELEPHONE?

00:54.500 --> 00:56.600
NO, RUBEN.
YOU'RE AHEAD OF YOUR TIME.

00:56.600 --> 00:57.800
ONE DAY EVERYBODY WILL HAVE

00:57.800 --> 01:00.700
ONE OF THESE... PORTABLE PHONES
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

01:00.700 --> 01:04.000
DON'T PATRONIZE ME!
DON'T YOU DO THAT!

01:04.000 --> 01:06.800
RUBEN, WAIT.
I KNOW HOW YOU'RE FEELING.

01:07.100 --> 01:08.700
I'VE LOST A LOT OF THINGS,
TOO.

01:08.700 --> 01:12.300
I KNOW IT CAN BE HARD TO FACE,
BUT YOU CAN GET THROUGH THIS.

01:12.300 --> 01:15.400
THAT'S GOOD, TYLER.
TALK TO HIM LIKE A WOMAN.

01:16.000 --> 01:17.400
AH, NO.

01:25.600 --> 01:26.800
WHAT'S THE MATTER, EUGENE?

01:26.800 --> 01:29.100
YOU CAN'T GET THE KITTY
OUT OF THE TREE? (laughs)

01:29.800 --> 01:33.500
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE,
NUNZIO?
WE JUST GOT CAME BACK

01:33.500 --> 01:35.000
WE HEARD THE CIRCUS
ON THE AIR,

01:35.000 --> 01:39.800
AND WE FIGURED WE'D COME
OVER HERE AND LEND A HAND.
WE DON'T NEED ANY HELP

01:39.800 --> 01:42.300
WHAT'S NEW, CARLING?
SAVE YOUR BREATH.

01:42.300 --> 01:44.400
YOU MIGHT NEED IT
TO BLOW UP YOUR DATE TONIGHT.

01:44.600 --> 01:46.800
OH!
THAT'S A GOOD ONE, CARBONE.

01:46.800 --> 01:50.100
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT YOUR WIFE
SAID TO ME AFTER SHE HOPPED OFF.

01:52.000 --> 01:54.300
HEY! ARE YOU LISTENING TO ME?

01:54.500 --> 01:56.500
I CAN'T GO BACK TO WHAT I HAD.

01:56.500 --> 02:00.700
MY BANK ACCOUNT SAYS ZERO.
I'M WORTH ZERO.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.400
(Ruben) NOW <i>I'M</i> A ZERO!
HEY, EUGENE,
WHY DON'T YOU TELL, UH,

02:03.400 --> 02:04.700
YOUR WEBELO TO GIVE ME THE HORN
OVER THERE?

02:04.700 --> 02:10.300
I'LL TALK THIS LOSER DOWN
BEFORE HAPPY HOUR.
SAM, WE DON'T HAVE TIME

02:10.300 --> 02:12.500
THIS GUY IS SUICIDAL.
I GOT IT.

02:12.500 --> 02:14.700
THIS ISN'T THE TIME
FOR SOME STUPID COP STUNT.

02:14.700 --> 02:18.200
THIS GUY IS SUICIDAL.
WHO'S YOUR, UH,
NEW CENTER FIELDER, EUGENE?

02:18.200 --> 02:22.200
SAM TYLER, TRANSFER.
TYLER, ANTHONY NUNZIO,

02:22.200 --> 02:24.500
THE HARVESTER OF SORROW.

02:24.500 --> 02:25.900
THIS IS NO STUNT,
SAM TYLER.

02:25.900 --> 02:28.200
I HAVE A PROVEN
PERSUASION TECHNIQUE.

02:28.800 --> 02:30.700
IT'S A NEW FORM
OF REVERSE PSYCHOLOGY,

02:30.700 --> 02:33.500
WHICH, WHEN, UH, USED
WITH HIGH-RISK NEGOTIATING,

02:33.500 --> 02:37.200
IS PROVING VERY EFFECTIVE.
WELL, WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,
LIEUTENANT,

02:37.200 --> 02:39.200
THERE'S NO WAY I'M LETTING YOU
TALK TO HIM.

02:39.400 --> 02:42.800
(Ruben) WHAT ARE YOU DOING
DOWN THERE? I'M GONNA JUMP.

02:42.800 --> 02:46.000
THIS IS IT!
WELL, YOU BETTER DO SOMETHING
REAL SOON, SAM TYLER,

02:46.000 --> 02:49.000
OR THIS GUY IS GONNA TURN
INTO GROUND GOO, TOUT SUITE.

02:49.600 --> 02:51.000
LET HIM HAVE A WHACK.

02:54.000 --> 02:55.200
AH, WHAT'S HIS NAME?

02:55.200 --> 02:57.800
RUBEN. WIFE LEFT HIM...

02:57.800 --> 03:00.000
AFTER HE LOST HIS SHIRT
IN THE STOCK MARKET...

03:00.000 --> 03:02.400
ON A PORTABLE PHONE COMPANY.

03:02.400 --> 03:04.100
WHO WANTS TO CARRY AROUND
A PHONE?
(scoffs)

03:05.400 --> 03:08.400
(Ruben) WHO ARE YOU?
(amplified voice)
HEY, RUBEN. HOW YOU DOING?

03:09.500 --> 03:11.400
GO AHEAD AND JUMP,
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

03:11.400 --> 03:14.500
YOU THINK WE GIVE A DAMN?
WHAT?!

03:14.500 --> 03:16.700
OH, BOSS.
NUNZIO.

03:16.700 --> 03:20.000
HEY, UH, YOUR WIFE CALLED...
ON THE PORTABLE PHONE.

03:20.000 --> 03:21.800
SHE CALLED TO TELL YOU
SHE SHACKED UP

03:21.800 --> 03:24.700
WITH THE GUY WHO INVENTED
THE PORTABLE RECORD PLAYER,

03:24.700 --> 03:27.100
AND SHE THINKS
YOU SHOULD JUMP, TOO.

03:27.100 --> 03:29.400
JUMP!
JUMP, YOU LOSER! JUMP!

03:29.400 --> 03:31.500
NUNZIO.
NO, DON'T DO IT, RUBEN!

03:33.500 --> 03:34.500
(crowd gasps)
(Sam) NO!

03:41.000 --> 03:42.900
WELP, I GUESS THIS, UH,

03:42.900 --> 03:45.900
REVERSE PSYCHOLOGY THING'S
GOT A WAYS TO GO.

