03:55.700 --> 03:57.100
 <i>MY NAME IS SAM TYLER.</i>

03:57.700 --> 04:01.100
 <i>I WAS IN AN ACCIDENT,</i>
 <i>AND I WOKE UP IN 1973.</i>

04:01.300 --> 04:03.200
 <i>I DON'T KNOW HOW OR WHY</i>
 <i>I'M HERE,</i>

04:03.400 --> 04:04.600
 <i>BUT WHATEVER'S HAPPENED,</i>

04:04.600 --> 04:06.700
 <i>IT'S LIKE I'VE LANDED</i>
 <i>ON A DIFFERENT PLANET.</i>

04:06.700 --> 04:10.500
 <i>NOW MAYBE IF I CAN WORK OUT</i>
 <i>THE REASON, I CAN GET HOME.</i>

