AT THE POLICEMAN'S BALL

31:07.000 --> 31:10.100
YOU TOLD THE CHIEF
MY SQUAD COULDN'T CLEAR PIMPLES.

31:10.100 --> 31:12.900
YOU SWIPED
THE BROWNSTONE ROBBERY--

31:12.900 --> 31:14.700
THE PUERTO RICANS?
AND BEFORE THAT,

31:14.700 --> 31:17.200
