THE KNIGHTS OF COLUMBUS? 1943.
I SAW HER FIRST. <i>I</i> CALLED SHOT.

31:23.400 --> 31:25.800
ANGELA WAS AN ADULT.

31:25.800 --> 31:28.600
YOU WANT ME TO TELL YOU
I'M SORRY SHE PICKED ME?

31:28.600 --> 31:29.800
