31:29.800 --> 31:32.600
AT GROWING BEETS
ON A TULIP FARM.

31:34.200 --> 31:36.100
I DON'T WANT AN APOLOGY.

31:36.100 --> 31:38.600
SEE, THE WAY I FIGURE IT,
I GOT ONE LESS BROKEN HEART

31:38.600 --> 31:41.500
BECAUSE OF YOU
SHUTTIN' OFF THOSE LIGHTS.

31:45.000 --> 31:47.600
THERE'S A FAMILY'S LIFE
AT STAKE HERE, ANTHONY.

31:47.600 --> 31:48.600
YEAH, THEY'RE RUSSKIES,

31:48.600 --> 31:52.400
BUT THAT DON'T MEAN THEY SHOULD
BE DENIED SOME FUN IN THE SUN.

31:52.400 --> 31:55.100
NOT ON OUR ACCOUNT, ANYWAYS.

32:03.700 --> 32:06.700
LUKIN OWNS THE APARTMENTS
ABOVE THE BATHHOUSE.

32:08.600 --> 32:10.300
I'D START THERE.

32:12.500 --> 32:15.100
