FOR LIEUTENANT HUNT.

32:30.900 --> 32:33.800
OH, I THINK HE'S OUT, UM,
ON A CASE.

32:33.800 --> 32:35.000
OH.

32:35.000 --> 32:36.600
YEP.
OKAY.

32:36.800 --> 32:38.800
HEY, NICE JOB TODAY.

32:40.400 --> 32:41.900
YABBA-DABBA-DO.

32:42.300 --> 32:43.600
IT WAS CUTE.

32:52.200 --> 32:53.500
ARE YOU SURE
YOU WANT TO DO THIS?

32:53.500 --> 32:56.300
OH, YEAH. I'M EMBRACING
MY IMMIGRANT STATUS.
OKAY.

33:01.000 --> 33:02.000
WAIT. WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

33:02.500 --> 33:03.900
SAFETY FIRST.
RIGHT.

33:20.000 --> 33:21.100
DINNER SOMETIME?

33:21.100 --> 33:22.800
I WOULD LIKE THAT.

33:28.600 --> 33:30.700
YOU'RE NICE, SAM TYLER.

33:30.700 --> 33:33.000
YES. I MEAN, YOU ARE...

33:33.500 --> 33:34.500
TOO.

33:38.200 --> 33:39.200
SO...

33:40.800 --> 33:41.600
HMM.

33:43.700 --> 33:45.600
HI.
HEY.

33:45.800 --> 33:47.900
YOU HAVE KETCHUP
OR SOMETHING.

33:48.500 --> 33:49.700
HMM? OH.

33:50.000 --> 33:52.000
YEAH. THANKS, I HAD, UH--
FRENCH FRIES.

33:52.000 --> 33:54.400
FRENCH FRIES. YES.

33:58.600 --> 34:00.600
I SHOULD, UM...
GO. THERE.

34:00.600 --> 34:01.900
YEAH.
GO.

34:04.500 --> 34:06.600
THERE YOU ARE, SPACEMAN.

34:06.600 --> 34:09.000
WE WERE ABOUT TO SEND OUT
THE BLOODHOUNDS.

34:09.000 --> 34:11.400
WELL, I STEPPED OUT
FOR SOME AIR.

34:12.000 --> 34:13.000
 <i>YEAH.</i>

34:13.900 --> 34:15.800
I GOTTA GET ME
SOME AIR LIKE THAT.

34:15.800 --> 34:16.900
LISTEN, WE FOUND OUT

34:16.900 --> 34:18.800
WHERE THE RUSSIANS
WERE KEEPING YURI'S FAMILY.

34:18.800 --> 34:21.300
THERE'S A, UH, APARTMENT
ABOVE THE <i>SCHVITZ.</i>

34:21.300 --> 34:23.300
SASHO WAS KEEPING
A CLOSE EYE ON 'EM.

34:23.500 --> 34:27.000
GOOD. UM... GOOD. LET'S GO.

34:29.600 --> 34:30.900
(Gene) VASILLI LUKIN.

34:31.800 --> 34:34.500
WHAT NOW... LIEUTENANT?

34:34.800 --> 34:38.300
I SENSE SARCASM IN THAT.
JUST CAME TO GIVE YOU SOME NEWS.

34:38.300 --> 34:41.699
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE
THE <i>SCHVITZ</i> IN ATTICA.

34:41.699 --> 34:45.000
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
FOR FELONY MURDER, SPUTNIK.

34:45.000 --> 34:48.500
MURDER?
THE DEAD WOMAN
FROM THE BANK ROBBERY?

34:48.500 --> 34:49.800
SEE, THE WAY
THE LAW WORKS IS,

34:49.800 --> 34:52.500
WHEN YOU THREATEN A GUY TO PAY
MONEY, AND THAT GUY ROBS A BANK

34:52.500 --> 34:56.800
AND SHOOTS SOMEONE,
THE BODY COMES BACK TO YOU.
NO PROOF.

34:56.800 --> 34:59.000
LIKE K.G.B.,
YOU FALSIFY STATEMENTS.

34:59.000 --> 35:02.600
ARE YOU GONNA
COME ALONG QUIETLY OR RESIST?

35:02.600 --> 35:05.500
