35:09.900 --> 35:13.600
IN MOSCOW, REAL POLICE
NEVER POINT GUNS.

35:13.600 --> 35:16.800
YOU WOULDN'T TALK SO MUCH,
BIG MOUTH,

35:16.800 --> 35:18.900
