ABSOLUTELY NOT.

35:23.300 --> 35:26.200
RAYMUNDO?
NOT WHEN I GOT
ALL TEN SOLDIERS.

35:26.200 --> 35:27.600
CHRISTOPHER GORDON SKELTON?

35:27.600 --> 35:28.700
NO, SIR. ALL TEN.
(slaps palm)

35:28.700 --> 35:30.400
(Gene) SIZEABLE?

35:30.400 --> 35:31.400
NO GUNS.

35:31.400 --> 35:35.200
AND ONE MORE THING, COMRADE.
VODKA IS FOR SISSIES.

35:35.200 --> 35:38.500
MEN DRINK WHISKEY.
